{"tid":1989740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"霍啟剛爭取盡快重開運動場地","createTime":"2020-04-26T07:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T08:20:50.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7ddd5ca5e315d63cfe95cd9eeef571571dc45a","tid":1989740,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"（星島日報報道）港協暨奧委會副會長霍啟剛近期頻頻發聲促請政府支援體育界，政府推出的第二輪防疫抗疫基金有回應訴求，惟被批評力度不足。霍啟剛日前跟新任民政事務局局長徐英偉會面（見圖），他直言感受到當局對體育界的重視，期望運動場地能盡快在有條件之下重開。<br />\n<br />\n  霍啟剛日前與新任民政事務局局長徐英偉會面，他及後在社交平台發文，感謝對方新上任就跟業界見面，更指感受到局方對體育界的重視。他透露：「席間大家都交換了很多關於重開康體場地的意見，&hellip;&hellip;希望在符合限聚令及有足夠防疫措施下，場地可以盡快開放，這能幫助教練，市民亦可以安心做運動。」<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2200200/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%9C%8D%E5%95%9F%E5%89%9B%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2200200%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%259C%258D%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%2589%259B%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%259C%25B0&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=9000be37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2200200%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%259C%258D%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%2589%259B%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%259C%25B0&h=16c548cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2200200/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%9C%8D%E5%95%9F%E5%89%9B%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0</a>"},{"pid":"39